DESCRIPTION:Savor SABOR & Support Sonoma Family Meal!\n\nSABOR Pop-up Lunc
 h Café is an opportunity for our culinary job training students to get ex
 perience working in a fast-paced environment “on the line” while raisi
 ng funds to keep our job training programs tuition-free. Each item on the 
 menu is a reflection of our students’ hard work\, creativity\, and the r
 ich culinary traditions they bring to the table. We invite you to come for
  lunch and support our students and our work to nourish the community\, cr
 eate opportunity\, and strengthen the local food ecosystem. There is limit
 ed seating\, so please plan to take food to go.\n\nWHEN: March 23-27 & Mar
 ch 30-April 1 \\(no weekends\\) | 11am-1pm WHERE: Petaluma kitchen\, 1370A
  Redwood Way\, Petaluma\, CA
