DESCRIPTION:Join us for **Stitch Café**\, a cozy open studio held twice a
  month. Whether you're working on your own project or eager to explore new
  mending techniques like darning and appliqué\, this is the perfect space
  to gather\, share ideas\, and sew together. We provide hand-sewing suppli
 es and materials\, but feel free to bring your own - it's all about commun
 ity\, creativity\, and enjoying the process. By repairing what we already 
 have and re-using materials\, we're not just preserving memories and addin
 g unique touches to our belongings - we’re also reducing waste and contr
 ibuting to a more sustainable lifestyle. We can extend the life of our clo
 thes and fabrics\, and take small but meaningful steps toward caring for t
 he planet.
LOCATION:Art Escape
URL:https://artescapesonoma.jumbula.com/Spring2026/StitchTogether401
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
