BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Sourdough Supper Club
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T210000
UID:260324c0kOp83NekOaQrawu0Ek9Q
DESCRIPTION:**Chicky & Dumplins**\n\nApril 2\, 2026\, 6 to 9 pm\n\nJoin Ja
 mes Beard Award-winning cookbook author Sarah Owens for a night of making 
 luscious Chicken n' Dumplings with sourdough starter. If you've been looki
 ng for ways to use your starter besides baking\, this is for you! Sarah wi
 ll show you how to make an unconventional roux and light and fluffy dumpli
 ngs\, both with sourdough starter\, for a fun spin on this classic Souther
 n comfort food. To conclude the evening\, you will enjoy a sit-down meal o
 f a small appetizer\, chicken and dumplings\, salad\, and a light dessert.
  The chicken and dumplings include dairy and meat. One glass of locally pr
 oduced wine or NA beverage is included. \n\n**Galette Night**\n\nApril 16
 \, 2026 6 to 9 pm\n\nJoin James Beard Award-winning cookbook author Sarah 
 Owens for a night of galette making using a wholegrain sourdough pie crust
 . If you've been looking for ways to use your sourdough starter besides br
 ead\, this is for you! Sarah will show you how to roll out and fill a flak
 y\, wholesome pie crust made with spelt and sourdough starter\, perfect fo
 r both sweet and savory fillings. While the galettes are baking\, Sarah wi
 ll demonstrate how to mix the pie crust and provide you with a recipe to m
 ake at home. To conclude the evening\, you will enjoy a sit-down meal of s
 oup\, a savory galette\, salad\, and a light dessert. The soup and galette
  are vegetarian\, but both include dairy. One glass of locally produced wi
 ne or NA beverage is included.
LOCATION:Drewish Deli
URL:https://ritualfinefoods.com/products/sourdough-supper-club
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Small Wonders
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T170000
UID:260324Q0A8Bhide0iBegXekpGAsw
DESCRIPTION:Call for Art: Small Wonders\n\nSome of the most exquisite beau
 ty can be captured in the smallest of images and objects: the iridescence 
 of a hummingbird in flight\, a millefiori paperweight\, Faberge eggs\, or 
 a miniature woven basket. These pieces are modest in size but powerful in 
 creativity and expression.\n\nHealdsburg Center for the Arts \\(HCA\\) inv
 ites artists to submit paintings\, original fine art prints\, collage\, mi
 xed media\, drawings\, fiber arts\, sculptures\, ceramics\, and jewelry fo
 r this exhibition.\n\nApplication Requirements:\n\n- Platform: All applica
 tions must be submitted via EntryThingy\n\n- Eligibility: Work must be ori
 ginal and completed within the past two years. Photos in the application m
 ust represent the actual work intended for exhibition.\n\n- Size/Weight: A
 rtwork must not exceed 12" x 12" unframed \\(144 sq in\\) or 196 sq in fra
 med. Maximum weight is 40 lbs.\n\n- Display: 2-D pieces must be securely w
 ired \\(no alligator clips\\). 3-D work must be stable\; artists are respo
 nsible for on-site assembly if required.\n\n- Sales: All work must be for 
 sale. HCA retains a 40% commission\; artists receive 60%. Please list reta
 il prices only.\n\nKey Dates:\n\n- Entry Deadline: May 10\, 2026 \\(9 PM\\
 )\n\n- Notification of Selection: By May 13\, 2026\n\n- Shipped Work Deadl
 ine: Wednesday\, May 27\, 2026 \\(must include pre-paid return label\\)\n\
 n- Hand-Delivery: Sunday\, May 31 \\(12–4 PM\\) and Monday\, June 1 \\(1
 1 AM–1 PM\\)\n\n- Exhibition Dates: June 4\, 2026 – July 19\, 2026\n\n
 - Opening Reception: Saturday\, June 6\, 2026 \\(4–6 PM\\)\n\n- Pick-up/
 Return Shipping: July 19 \\(12–4 PM\\) and July 20 \\(11 AM–1 PM\\)\; 
 shipping the week of July 20.\n\nEntry Fees:\n\n- Non-Members: $50 \\(1 en
 try\\)\, $55 \\(2 entries\\)\, $60 \\(3 entries\\). Includes a $60 yearly 
 supporter membership.\n\n- Current Members: $40 \\(1 entry\\)\, $45 \\(2 e
 ntries\\)\, $50 \\(3 entries\\).
LOCATION:Healdsburg Center for the Arts
URL:https://healdsburgcenterforthearts.org/small-wonders-2/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
