DESCRIPTION:Bring your curiosity and an open mind and join us for a Death 
 Café Napa where friends and strangers come together in a relaxed\, safe a
 nd supportive setting to talk about death and dying while enjoying tea & s
 weets. Conversation is group-directed with no set agenda\, theme or object
