SUMMARY:Friday Night Comedy - Ronn Vigh - Downtown Santa Rosa
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T220000
UID:260329yPjalHGNLkOYnGoYuQDdag
DESCRIPTION:Friday night stand-up comedy in Downtown Santa Rosa\n\nVIP TAB
 LES NOW AVAILABLE! Snag a table for 4 with preferred seating\, your own pr
 ivate call button to summon service\, and your first round of drinks (or a
  bottle of wine) for only $95!\n\nEvery Friday night hilarious comedians f
 rom The Bay Area and beyond perform at Barrel Proof Lounge. Stick around a
 fter for late-night karaoke!\n\nFresh lineup of funny each Friday.\n\nThis
  Week: Jon Lehre (host) Nate Schwartz Molly Sokhom Headliner: Ronn Vigh\n\
 nEarly in his career\, Ronn Vigh's brash attitude and acerbic wit earned h
 im a comparison to a young Joan Rivers by the SF Weekly. It was certainly 
 a fitting comparison as Ronn later became a writer for Rivers on her hit E
 ! Television show "Fashion Police." Ronn regularly performs at comedy club
 s\, colleges and festivals across the nation. He also co-hosts the sports-
 comedy podcast\, "Switching Teams: A Gay Dude & A Straight Dude Talk About
  Sports."\n\nHis biggest accomplishment: Working briefly as a flight atten
 dant and not attempting to smother any of his passengers with a pillow. Ye
 s\, there were complimentary pillows on the plane when Ronn did that job. 
 Please don't do the math. IG @ronnronnronn\n\n21+ Doors - 7p / Show - 8p $
 15adv / $20door\n\nCheck out **www.BarrelProofLounge.com** for all sorts
  of good times ahead.
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/friday-night-comedy-ronn-vigh-downtown-sa
 nta-rosa-tickets-1982249113459?aff=oddtdtcreator
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Ancient Secrets of Natural Healing with Ayurveda
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T200000
UID:2603281mkOvehr0UejKxK6M-ye3w
DESCRIPTION:Experience Ayurveda with Ayushakti\, a globally trusted organi
 zation serving clients across 108\\+ countries for over 35 years.\n\nIn th
 is special workshop hosted in collaboration with Ayushakti Clinic Partner 
 Dhyana\, Vaidya Ronak Naik will introduce Ayurveda’s timeless principles
  and demonstrate how they can be applied in simple\, practical ways to sup
 port balance\, vitality\, and overall well-being in today’s fast-paced w
 orld.\n\nAttending this Ayurveda workshop offers a unique opportunity to g
 ain practical\, time-tested tools for improving personal well-being\, even
  for those new to Ayurveda or unfamiliar with its foundational concepts.\n
 \nWhat is Ayurveda and Why Is It Beneficial?\n\nAyurveda is a holistic hea
 lth system from India practiced for over 5\,000 years\, emphasizing balanc
 e in the body\, mind\, and spirit through personalized diet\, routine\, he
 rbal remedies\, and lifestyle choices. Its principles focus on preventing 
 illness\, promoting vibrant health\, and helping individuals understand th
 eir unique constitution or “dosha” to maintain harmony with nature.\n\
 nSpecial Features of This Workshop\n\n- Global Expertise: Benefit from the
  guidance of Vaidya Ronak Naik\, who has trained widely in India and abroa
 d\, bringing deep proficiency in foundational Ayurvedic techniques includi
 ng pulse assessment\, detox therapies\, and natural healing methods.\n\n- 
 Interactive\, Practical Learning: Participate in live demonstrations\, dis
 cussions\, and activities that translate ancient theory into modern\, acti
 onable steps suitable for today’s lifestyle.\n\n- Supportive Community S
 etting: Connect with like-minded wellness seekers in a nurturing environme
 nt\, fostering motivation and meaningful learning.\n\nBy attending\, parti
 cipants not only gain evidence-informed tools for everyday use but also a 
 richer perspective on their health journey\, guided by experts who bridge 
 traditional and practical modern wellness approaches.\n\nAlongside the wor
 kshop\, participants will also have the rare opportunity to book individua
 l consultations with Vaidya Ronak. These one-on-one sessions provide a cha
 nce to discuss your unique health concerns and explore how personalized Ay
 urvedic recommendations may support your wellness journey.\n\nAbout Vaidya
  Ronak Naik\n\nVaidya Ronak Naik\, Senior Ayurvedic Practitioner\, is a hi
 ghly trained Ayurvedic practitioner with over 11 years of experience in Ay
 urveda and Panchakarma. A graduate of Rajiv Gandhi University of Health Sc
 iences\, Mangalore \\(2008\\)\, he began his journey with Ayushakti soon a
 fter completing his studies. Undergoing two years of intensive training wi
 th senior Ayushakti Vaidyas\, he developed expertise in pulse assessment\,
  Panchakarma detoxification\, and Marma techniques.\n\nHe regularly travel
 s to Ayushakti centers in the USA and Europe to offer consultations and Pa
 nchakarma programs and has shared his knowledge by training over 30 practi
 tioners in pulse assessment and Ayurvedic methodologies.\n\nVaidya Ronak i
 s deeply committed to guiding individuals on their journey toward improved
  balance and well-being through time-tested Ayurvedic wisdom.\n\nAbout Dhy
 ana Bohnet\n\nDhyana Bohnet\, Clinic Partner\, Ayurvedic Praactitioner & V
 edic Astrologer\, draws from over 40 dedicated years experience as a holis
 tic practitioner and wellness professional. Her love of Ayurveda began ove
 r 17 years ago while traversing the peaks and valleys of her own transform
 ative healing journey. She now specializes in eastern holistic modalities\
 , including Ayurveda\, Vedic Astrology and Daoist Qigong energy practices.
 \n\nWith healing hands she also offers Ayurveda treatments and cranial-sac
 ral therapy.
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/vaidya-ronak/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
