DESCRIPTION:**MERCY PRESENTS:**\n\n**Last Mic Standing: Comedy Showdown**\
 n\n**Battle for the Main Stage.**\n\nOn **Friday\, April 3rd from 8PM – 
 9:30PM**\, eight fearless comics step into the spotlight for one night of 
 rapid-fire punchlines\, crowd reactions\, and high-stakes humor inside The
  Lounge at Mercy.\n\nThis isn’t an open mic.\n\nThis is a showdown.\n\n*
 *8 Comics. 3 Judges. Audience Vote.**\n\nEach comedian brings their sharpe
 st material and strongest stage presence to compete for the title of Last 
 Mic Standing. Judges score the sets. The crowd weighs in. The energy decid
 es everything.\n\nOne night. One winner.\n\nThe stakes are real. The winne
 r takes home a $100 cash prize and earns a paid hosting spot at the next M
 ercy’s Tokes & Jokes Comedy Night. Win the crowd. Own the mic. Come back
  as host.\n\nComics sign up here & get a free entry to the event: https://
 bit.ly/lastmicsignup Names will be drawn from a hat day of the event.\n\nT
 his is a 420-friendly comedy competition hosted inside our fully licensed 
 cannabis consumption lounge\, where elevated vibes meet elevated punchline
 s. Guests are welcome to enjoy responsibly while comics go head-to-head un
 der the lights. Great sets hit different here.\n\n**Ticket Tiers**\n\n**$2
 0 — General Admission (Open Seating)** Entry to Comedy Showdown 🎤 Ope
 n seating (first come\, first served). Come early for the best spot.\n\n**
 $30 — GA + Goodie Bag** A little extra ✨ Entry + goodie bag ($15 value
 ) included. Open seating (first come\, first served). \n\n**⭐ $40 — P
 referred Bucket Seat + Goodie Bag (Most Popular)** Comfort upgrade ⭐ Gua
 ranteed bucket seat + shared table access\, plus goodie bag ($15 value) in
 cluded. Limited seating.\n\n**🔥 $135 — Couch Crew Pass (3 Guests + Pr
 emium Bag)** Bring your crew 🔥 Includes admission for 3 guests\, reserv
 ed couch seating with a dedicated table\, plus premium bag ($100 value) in
 cluded. **Only 11 couches.**\n\n21+ Only | DCC # C12-0000420-LIC
LOCATION:The Lounge at Mercy
URL:https://eventhi.io/events/last-mic-standing-comedy-showdown-4326-13896
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
