BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Sacred Sounds Series with Yogetsu Akasaka
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T210000
UID:260324ifWjMLSy5U6vlG7Nj8ln4Q
DESCRIPTION:Join Zen priest and live-looping artist Yogetsu Akasaka for a 
 meditative sound journey awakening the healing power of your voice. Throug
 h breathwork\, vocal toning\, and 432Hz improvised loops\, Yogetsu creates
  a space where silence and vibration meet. This workshop is not about sing
 ing beautifully—it is about listening deeply to the vibration within and
  discovering how your own hum\, tone\, or mantra can calm the nervous syst
 em\, release stored emotions\, and open a space of profound stillness ofte
 n described as emptiness or void in Zen.
LOCATION:Spirit Rock Meditation Center
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/sacred-sounds-series-wi
 th-yogetsu-akasaka/18363168/2026-04-03T19
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
