DESCRIPTION:Carol Menke will direct Cantiamo Sonoma and the Roses Choir fo
 r our Good Friday concert at the Presbyterian Church of the Roses in Santa
  Rosa.  This year’s offering is the stunning ***Requiem*** by contem
 porary American composer\, Michael John Trotta.  Mr. Trotta describes *
 **Requiem*** as “a prayer for those who have gone before us\, for those
  that are left behind\, and a prayer that all of us may find peace when fa
 cing the unknown.”  Join us for an evening of profoundly inspirational
  music.
