DESCRIPTION:**Russian River Railbikes – Easter Weekend Experience** Elev
 ate your Easter weekend with an enjoyable railbike journey through the hea
 rt of Sonoma County. Glide along historic railway lines to the Russian Riv
 er\, surrounded by rolling vineyards\, blooming wildflowers\, and serene s
 pring landscapes to the turn around point overlooking the Russian River wi
 th picnic tables and Easter surprises for kids.\n\n**📅 When:** Easter 
 Weekend (Saturday & Sunday departures) **⏱ Duration:** Approximately 1.
 5–2 hours\, including a riverside pause **👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Rail
 bikes:** Accommodates 2–4 guests per bike **💲 Cost:** From ~$45 per
