DESCRIPTION:KPFZ\, Lake County Community Radio presents:\n\nTempest   Cel
 tic Rock Concert\n\nSaturday\, April 4\, 2026  7:00pm  Doors open at 6:3
 0\n\n"Celtic music rock and roll band Tempest returns to Lake County. This
  high energy band will have you dancing and clapping to the music. This is
  a benefit for KPFZ Lake County Community Radio."\n\nTempest is a Bay Area
  high energy Celtic rock band that has been performing for over 35 years i
 n the U.S.  This band fuses Irish reels\, Scottish Ballads\, and Norwegia
 n influences into their rock music. \n\nOpen Seating.  $30.00 at the Door
 .  $25.00 in Advance
