 with an egg hunt through the vineyards\, followed by a festive carnival at
  the winery with games and entertainment for all ages. The Easter Bunny wi
 ll be on-site for photos\, adding to the celebration. Guests are encourage
 d to arrive between 10:00 and 10:45am to ensure they don't miss the hunt. 
 Please bring a basket for collecting eggs and treats. Ticket purchases are
  limited to 12 per guest. No tickets are required for guests ages 13 and u
 p. The Pool Café will be open with a special à la carte menu featuring f
 ood and beverages.
