DESCRIPTION:This program is presented in Spanish. Spanish Music & Movement
  is a tour of culture\, language\, and fun! This presentation is not for s
 itting - your family will be active characters in these adventures\, parti
 cipating with colorful scarves\, instruments\, and animals as you move to 
 the sound of language. Even if you are not fluent Spanish speakers\, see t
 he language come alive through the animated and energetic activities desig
 ned for children under 6 years and family.
