DESCRIPTION:*A Full Easter Experience for the Whole Family*\n\nJoin us for
  a joyful Easter celebration at the **Sonoma County Fairgrounds in Santa R
 osa**. It’s more than a service — it’s a full family experience. Com
 e early\, stay after\, and enjoy a relaxed\, fun atmosphere together.\n\n*
 *Two Easter Services** 9:00 AM & 11:00 AM\n\n**Indoor Egg Hunts All Mornin
 g**\n\nWhat to Expect\n\n• Local food trucks • Free coffee • Free fa
 mily photos\n\nKids & Family Activities\n\n• Indoor Easter egg hunts thr
 oughout the morning • Bunny petting zoo • Secure kids & family areas 
 • Friendly safety team on site\n\nOur **indoor egg hunts** happen in org
 anized sessions so every child can enjoy the experience in a calm\, safe e
 nvironment — and every child goes home with a candy bag.\n\nBring your f
 amily\, invite your friends\, and celebrate Easter together.
LOCATION: Sonoma County Fairgrounds
URL:https://www.thepromisecenter.com/easter?utm_source=pressdemocrat&utm_m
 edium=events&utm_campaign=Easter
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Celebrate Easter with the Russian River Railbikes
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T150000
UID:260328iEAf4hx95UibkTNnofI0Mw
DESCRIPTION:**Russian River Railbikes – Easter Weekend Experience** Elev
 ate your Easter weekend with an enjoyable railbike journey through the hea
 rt of Sonoma County. Glide along historic railway lines to the Russian Riv
 er\, surrounded by rolling vineyards\, blooming wildflowers\, and serene s
 pring landscapes to the turn around point overlooking the Russian River wi
 th picnic tables and Easter surprises for kids.\n\n**📅 When:** Easter 
 Weekend (Saturday & Sunday departures) **⏱ Duration:** Approximately 1.
 5–2 hours\, including a riverside pause **👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Rail
 bikes:** Accommodates 2–4 guests per bike **💲 Cost:** From ~$45 per
  guest or ~$145 per railbike\n\nAn ideal escape for couples\, families\, o
 r small groups seeking a distinctive and elevated outdoor experience. Avai
 lability is limited for the holiday weekend—early reservations are stron
 gly encouraged.
LOCATION:Russian River Railbikes
URL:http://www.russianriverrailbikes.org
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Monthly Sound Journey Experience
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T170000
UID:260328CCslTa1WVEGvItAawAUIVg
DESCRIPTION:This month\, we welcome Suzanne Renee Smith\, more formally kn
 own as The Celestial Voice.\n\nSound healing creates the space for self-he
 aling and transformation using the power of vibration to re-harmonize the 
 entire body to its most beneficial state. When we hear the frequencies\, o
 ur cells become attuned to that vibration and this creates a harmonic stat
 e for healing within the body. The different frequencies emanated during t
 he sound bath will help to quiet the mind\, decrease stress and anxiety\, 
 improve sleep\, release physical and emotional pain\, restoring the body\,
  mind and spirit to a greater state of balance\, creating a deeper sense o
 f peace and well-being.\n\nAbout Suzanne\n\nSuzanne Renee Smith\, The Cele
 stial Voice\, has been working with sound as a healing medium since 2008 i
 n Vienna Austria where she lived and worked as a professional singer\, mus
 ician\, song and copy writer\, voice over talent for radio and TV commerci
 als and vocal instructor\, from 1990 to 2009.\n\nIn 2007\, prompted by the
  loss of her voice for 4 months\, due to a paralyzed vocal cord she was le
 d by the Angelic realms\, in a spontaneous channeling\, to rediscover\, an
 d repurpose\, her voice as a conduit of healing energy beginning with her 
 first Crystal bowl played in the Great Pyramid and temples of Egypt on a j
 ourney in 2008. After traveling around the world in 2009 & 2010\, alone an
 d to herself\, for 1 year\, she moved to Sebastopol\, California.\n\nShe h
 as been working regularly in and around Sonoma County\, as a Sound Healer\
 , predominately\, since 2016. She has worked extensively with Cassiopiea S
 kyfish\, the Blue Muse\, leading Sound Baths in local Community Centers an
 d Yoga Studios\, at IONS the Institute of Noetic Sciences\, Osmosis Sanctu
 ary\, to the San Francisco Botanical Gardens and for Corporate retreats un
 der the Redwoods in Yosemite and Armstrong Woods\, CA.\n\nFor a sample of 
 Suzanne's Celestial Sound visit: https://www.thecelestialvoice.com/gallery
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/reset-renew/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
