 ain Cemetery Tour\, hosted by the Sonoma Valley Historical Society. Hear s
 tories of local legends\, from a vintner who used 6\,000 gallons of wine t
 o fight the 1911 fire to a trailblazer who launched a thriving industry. T
 ours run mid-morning to early afternoon in small groups\, beginning at the
  Mountain Cemetery water fountain. Expect steep terrain\; proper footwear\
 , water\, and optional walking sticks are recommended. Parking is availabl
