 k playing original music is starting to pay off. His work ethic and drive 
 is making this North Bay native a fast rising star beyond local circles an
 d his ever growing fan base gives him no reason to slow down. Inspiration 
 and his continued pursuit to share messages of love and longing mixed with
  an edge that stems from part vintage - part modern approach to writing an
 d production there's no telling\, but the best is yet to come for this you
 ng writer. \n\nSebastian has been voted People's Choice Best Performer in 
