UID:260327ujL6pwVg90CuIwW6XkUahQ
DESCRIPTION:This is an intimate community center show at the Monan's Rill 
 Community Center in Santa Rosa. Doors are at 7pm and music starts at 8pm. 
 Suggested ticket is $35 but is sliding scale starting at $25. Please pay m
 ore if you can. All money goes directly to the artist and there are no tic
 ket fees. About Monan's Rill: The Rill is an intentional\, intergeneration
 al community in rural Sonoma County\, California. We hold a shared commitm
 ent to the land we live on\, to core community values\, and to one another
 .\n\nPlease pay close attention to the directions and parking info below. 
 Monan’s Rill is located at 7899 Saint Helena Road\, Santa Rosa 95404. On
 ce you turn off St Helena Rd at 7899 \\(big yellow mailbox\\) and get onto
  the gravel road\, please keep your speed below 15 mph. There will be a fe
 w forks in the road -- go LEFT at the first fork \\(sign for 7899\\). At t
 he second fork \\(entrance to Monan's Rill\\)\, those who have capacity to
  walk on variable terrain should take a LEFT at the second fork\, then rig
 ht at the "parking" sign for our large event parking area. Park in the mar
 ked areas\, then walk to the HUB \\(5 minute walk\\). For anyone who has a
 ccess needs\, take a right at the second fork instead\, and left at the th
 ird fork \\(follow signs for the HUB\\). There is more limited parking ava
 ilable directly adjacent to the HUB.
LOCATION:Monan's Rill Community Hub
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/108106137?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
