UID:2603211FxhvrwsEUG-3t4iEscMNw
DESCRIPTION:Schedule\n\nFriday\, April 10\, 2026 5:00 PM – 8 :00 PM\n\nL
 ocation\n\nRoom 109\, Rotary Kitchen\n\nExperience Level\n\nAll Levels\n\n
 Event Category: Culinary Arts\n\nAge(s)\n\n18 and older\n\nRegistration Co
 st:\n\n$100\n\nMaterials Fee:\n\nProvided\n\nTotal Registration Cost:\n\n*
 *$100**\n\nPâte à Choux – Parisian Pastries About the Class One dough\
 , six pastries! Pate a choux is an exceptionally versatile dough. In this 
 class I will show you how to…\n\nAbout the Class\n\nOne dough\, six past
 ries! Pate a choux is an exceptionally versatile dough. In this class I wi
 ll show you how to make six sweet and savory Parisian pastries all with th
 e same dough! I will also show how\, if stored properly\, this dough can b
 e your secret weapon for a last minute dinner\, surprise guests\, or somet
 hing to impress at any gathering! We will go through each step together pr
 eparing the dough\, piping\, cooking\, and finishing. In addition\, we wil
 l fill\, glaze\, and garnish the pastries to take home. After all the fun\
 , enjoy a salad with Parisian gnocchi\, no surprise\, also made with pate 
 a choux dough! I am so excited to show you this amazing recipe that you wi
 ll be able to use for years and years to come!
