DESCRIPTION:Documentary Film and Performance. Join us in celebration for a
  screening of Skin to Skin\, followed by a conversation with John Santos i
 n honor of the power of music and inclusion. SANTOS–Skin to Skin is a fi
 lm portrait of community activist and seven-time Grammy nominee John Sant
 os\, a “keeper of the Afro-Caribbean flame.” Rich in musical performan
 ces\, Santos links the rhythms of his ancestors to contemporary struggles 
 of identity and social justice. A discussion with filmmaker Kathryn Golden
  and a live performance with the John Santos Quartet will directly follow 
 the screening.
LOCATION:Jarvis Conservatory
