BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Smartphone Food Photography with Dawn Heumann at Gold Ridge Organi
 c Farms
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T143000
UID:26031329sW_bk-lEOSxcBNlGbmbA
DESCRIPTION:Want to take better photos for your social media accounts with
 out hiring a pro every time?\n\nJoin award-winning commercial photographer
  and director Dawn Heumann for an immersive\, 90-minute\, hands-on worksho
 p and learn practical tips and tricks to elevate your everyday content—u
 sing mostly the camera on your phone.\n\nYou’ll discover how to find and
  use natural light\, understand how lighting affects mood\, and learn how 
 to bring it all together to showcase and celebrate your brand. We’ll als
 o cover simple tools\, editing techniques\, and content strategies to help
  your brand feel more consistent\, beautiful\, and authentic.No fancy gear
  required—just your phone\, your eye\, and a little curiosity.\n\nWhat y
 ou’ll learn:\n\n\\*How to find and use great light\n\n\\*Simple tricks f
 or shooting food and products\n\n\\*Tools that make mobile photography eas
 ier\n\n\\*Social media tips for visual consistency\n\n\\*Easy editing apps
  and workflows\n\n\\*Hands-on practice and real-time feedback\n\nSet in ou
 r charming Apple Cottage\, this workshop is ideal for personal brand build
 ers\, side hustlers\, small business owners\, or anyone eager to create sc
 roll-stopping content. It also includes a round-trip ride in our apple-the
 med trolley between the Farm Shop and Apple Cottage\, plus a 10% discount 
 on all Farm Shop purchases on the day of the workshop.\n\nDawn Heumann is 
 a commercial photographer and director with nearly 20 years of experience 
 creating award-winning content for global food\, beverage\, and lifestyle 
 brands. Based in Sonoma County\, she specializes in natural\, human-center
 ed storytelling that captures the heart of a brand.
LOCATION:Gold Ridge Organic Farms
URL:https://www.exploretock.com/gold-ridge-organic-farms/event/597325/smar
 tphone-food-photography-workshop-with-dawn-heumann
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
