DESCRIPTION:***Spirit Guides: Fantastical Creatures from the Workshop of J
 acobo and María Ángeles*** features brightly colored\, richly patterned
  sculptures depicting imaginary hybrid animals that serve as spirit guides
  and astrological embodiments of human character. Inspired by the Zapotec 
 calendar\, the exhibition includes eight large-scale works organized by De
 nver Botanic Gardens.
