UID:260327Dr0jwZtzUEG_8qg7ke-nyQ
DESCRIPTION:THE TAHOES RETURN TO RIO NIDO ROADHOUSE 🔥\n\nThey're Back t
 o Shake the Redwoods!\n\nRIO NIDO – GET READY TO RUMBLE\n\nThe wait is O
 VER! Sonoma County's most explosive rock/funk/punk/reggae powerhouse is ma
 king their triumphant return to the iconic Rio Nido Roadhouse\, and they'r
 e about to turn the Russian River upside down!\n\n⚡ THE COMEBACK THE ROA
 DHOUSE DESERVES ⚡\n\nAfter absolutely destroying this legendary venue la
 st time\, The Tahoes are back to prove they've only gotten better. If you 
 were there before\, you know what's about to go down. If you missed it –
  don't make that mistake twice.\n\n🎸 12 YEARS OF WEST COAST DOMINATION.
  ONE UNFORGETTABLE NIGHT. 🎸\n\nFrom sharing stages with Sublime with Ro
 me\, 311\, The Wailers\, and Fishbone to leveling iconic venues like DNA L
 ounge\, Bottom of the Hill\, and the High Times Cannabis Cup – The Tahoe
 s have earned their reputation as one of the West Coast's most electrifyin
 g live acts.\n\nNOW THEY'RE BRINGING THAT THUNDER BACK TO THE ROADHOUSE\n\
 nGet ready for:\n\n✓ Original bangers that'll rattle the rafters\n\n✓ 
 Crowd-crushing covers that pack the dance floor\n\n✓ Non-stop energy fro
 m first note to last call\n\n✓ The kind of night that becomes Rio Nido l
 egend\n\n🌲 THE REDWOODS ARE ABOUT TO SHAKE 🌲\n\nCircle the date. Gra
 b your crew. Spread the word. The Tahoes are returning to Rio Nido Roadhou
 se\, and it's going to be absolutely EPIC.\n\nSEE YOU AT THE ROADHOUSE –
  LET'S ROCK THE RIVER! 🎶🍺
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/107930478?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
