DESCRIPTION:Cuban Salsa Class with Eric Celestino & Abigail Celestino\n\nT
 his is a beginner-to-intermediate level class\, and all levels are welcome
  — we structure the class in a way that supports everyone in the same sp
 ace.\n\nIn this class\, you will learn the fundamentals of Cuban Salsa\, i
 ncluding body movement\, rhythm\, musicality\, footwork\, partner connecti
 on\, and partnerwork patterns inspired by authentic Cuban dance culture. W
 e focus on proper technique\, coordination\, flow\, and natural body expre
 ssion\, while also building confidence and strong foundations.\n\nClasses 
 are structured with:\n\nWarm-up and body movement\n\nFootwork and rhythm e
 xercises\n\nPartnerwork technique\n\nShort combinations and practical appl
 ications\n\nOur goal is to help you understand how to dance salsa\, not ju
 st memorize steps — developing timing\, connection\, and a comfortable\,
  joyful way of dancing.\n\nCome dance with us\, grow your technique\, and 
 experience the energy and flavor of Cuba in a supportive and welcoming env
 ironment.\n\nBook your spot\n\nDate & Time:\n\nMondays @ 6:00 PM\n\nAddres
 s: 4140 Redwood Highway \\#8 San Rafael\, CA\n\nNote: Arrive 10 minutes be
 fore. No floor marking shoe soles allowed.
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/cuban-salsa/18336477/20
 26-04-13T18
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Move N Groove
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260413T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260413T170000
UID:260319xBcV9nwh9UK_6W7Ov0_WWw
DESCRIPTION:Find Your Rhythm with James Darling Looking for a fun way to 
 stay active? Join James for a fun dance session designed for everyone. We
 ’re turning up the volume on the world’s biggest pop hits—come expre
 ss yourself and leave it all on the floor!\n\nNo stress: Every song uses 
 repetitive moves so you’ll be a pro by the final chorus.\n\nGet confiden
 t: We rotate the same playlist all month long\, giving you plenty of time
  to master the groove.\n\nJoin the party!\n\nAt Move N Groove\, we care m
 ore about your smile than your footwork. This isn’t just a cardio dance 
 class\; it’s a high-energy trip through musical theater\, world beats\, 
 and your favorite hits from every decade.\n\nCome sweat\, laugh\, and danc
 e like nobody’s watching.\n\nAbout James\n\nPutting the fun in fitness f
 or over 30 years!\n\nI’ve been teaching and developing challenging class
 es that put the joy in enjoyment. Our bodies need to keep moving to mainta
 in balance\, strength\, flexibility\, and so much more. Why not make it fu
 n?\n\nThe more we move the better we feel. It’s proven that the only way
  to keep your body in tip top shape is to keep going. So why not have a fa
 bulous time while doing it? Come to class and see how your thoughts on mov
 ement will shift towards a happier more fulfilled experience at the gym.\n
 \nDATE AND TIME: Mondays\, 4:00 PM
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
URL:https://salsadancemarin.com/classes/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
