 oration of multimedia finishing techniques that add a creative spin to you
 r ceramic work.\n\nAbout the Class\n\nExpand your definition of functional
  ceramics through the exploration of multimedia adornments and attachments
 . Lynn Wood will take the students through the material exploration of add
 ing wire\, metal\, twigs\, cording\, and more to your ceramic pieces. Stud
 ents will be educated on material that can be applied pre-firing\, as well
  as cold finishing processes \\(the addition of non-clay material after th
 e piece has fired\\).\n\nGet 20% off when you sign up for both Handbuildin
 g workshops\n\nIf you register for Dive Deeper as well as Handbuilt Pots y
 ou can receive 20% off your total registration cost. Both classes are on t
 he same day and run April 1 – May 6. There will be a 30 minute break bet
 ween sessions. You can call the front desk at \\(707\\) 938-4626 or email 
 sean@sonomacommunitycenter.org to receive the discount.
LOCATION:Sonoma Community Center
URL:https://sonomacommunitycenter.org/programs/handbuilt-pots-with-multime
 dia-adornments/
