DESCRIPTION:Sol Horizon opens for Grammy Award winner Kabaka Pyramid & The
  Bebble Rockers at Sebastopol Community Cultural Center on THURSDAY\, APRI
 L 16TH!\n\nSol Horizon has been Sonoma County\, California’s premier reg
 gae band for the past 25 years. The band was voted “Best Band” in the 
