DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260416T193000
UID:251120BWqFhSFj2kupON7yKoNyfQ
DESCRIPTION:This monthly gathering meets every third Thursday of each mont
 h. We have the intention of offering a safe space for all men who walk a p
 ath of seeking authenticity. Led by Collin Hoctor\, this group brings comm
 unity\, shares wisdom\, and brings healing to those who desire to walk a d
 eeper\, more meaningful life.\n\nFrom Collin:\n\nI am a psychotherapist an
 d guide whose work weaves together spirituality\, nature-based practices\,
  psychedelic therapy\, and recovery. My path has been shaped by a foundati
 on in existential philosophy and psychology\, medicine circles\, and a lif
 elong study of contemplative and esoteric traditions. Out of my own longin
 g for community and a commitment to the needs of the moment\, I am passion
 ate about creating spaces for men to gather in honesty\, vulnerability\, a
 nd authenticity — places where we can face our struggles\, share our tru
 ths\, and remember the healing power of connection.
LOCATION:The Unstruck Drum - Center for Shamanism
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/monthly-men-s-circle-3r
 d-thursday/17343490/2026-04-16T18
