BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Johnny & June Forever
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260417T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260417T000000
UID:260327nmaxuHLBKkaE706zSy2dgA
DESCRIPTION:From his \\#1 hit “I Walk the Line” in 1956 to the iconic 
 “Folsom Prison Blues\,” many have known and loved Johnny Cash over the
  years. Over 90 million records sold! No love\, though\, seems as great as
  the love that singer/songwriter June Carter had for Cash during their lon
 g years together. Though they have passed on\, the passion that burned bet
 ween them will always be present in their heartfelt and truthful lyrics wr
 itten and performed for one another. As one of the most beloved couples in
  music history\, Johnny Cash and June Carter Cash’s love lives on throug
 h their iconic duos and many albums recorded with each other.  \n\n   \n\n
 Johnny Cash and June Carter were well known performers before meeting\, an
 d like their predecessors\, Danny Evans and Essence of ‘Johnny & June Fo
 rever’ are also seasoned artists in their own rights. Their chemistry an
 d musicality on stage is so undeniable that many have described them as th
 e reincarnation of Johnny & June.\n\nOnline Dinner Reservations from 6:00p
 m - 8:00 pm \\(Please make a note of your dinner reservation time\\)\n\nMu
 sic @ 7:30pm\n\nTicket price is for admission only. Dinner is not included
  in the ticket price.\n\nBring your photo ID & ticket confirmation to Will
  Call.\n\nALL TICKET SALES ARE FINAL. No refunds or exchanges
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/108077417?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
