BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Enchanted April at Maison Louise
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T150000
UID:260325AjKVwykSWkmi-Y3mh4Ackg
DESCRIPTION:Join SVMA for a special Great Places | Great Spaces fundraisin
 g event at the breathtaking Maison Louise in Glen Ellen\, hosted by Teresa
  L. Johnson. Saturday\, April 18\, 3-5:00 PM Maison Louise\, Glen Ellen $2
 00 per person | Space is limited. Tickets are nonrefundable Set against sw
 eeping views of the Sonoma Mountains\, this intimate gathering takes place
  at the height of spring\, when prolific wisteria vines cascade across the
  property\, framing the landscape and softening the transition between ind
 oors and out. Inside the home\, a thoughtfully curated collection of conte
 mporary art reveals an ongoing dialogue between artists and collectors\, o
 ne rooted in curiosity\, personal connection\, and the evolving life of ar
 tworks beyond the gallery. Guests will have the opportunity to meet two ar
 tists featured in the Maison Louise collection\, Oli Kellett and Coral Woo
 dbury\, both represented by HackelBury Fine Art in London.
LOCATION:Sonoma Valley Museum of Art
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/1753735095789322/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
