BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Calistoga Art Center's Annual Souper Bowl #16
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T210000
UID:260303JGh0sODTGk-duvjxKZPkFA
DESCRIPTION:CALISTOGA \\(February 21\, 2026\\) – Now in its 16th year\, 
 Calistoga Art Center’s popular Souper Bowl fundraiser will be held on Sa
 turday\, April 18\, at the Boys & Girls Club of Calistoga.  Tickets are n
 ow on sale\, and event sponsorships are available.\n\nSouper Bowl gets its
  name from the unique pairing of gourmet soups from local restaurants with
  handmade ceramic bowls crafted by CAC’s talented instructors and studen
 ts. Guests choose from over 250 artisan bowls which they take home at the 
 end of the evening. Many prize their collection of bowls from past events.
  Each year\, Souper Bowl guests vote for their favorite soup of the night.
  Last year’s winner was Lovina for its luscious asparagus bisque. \n\nS
 ouper Bowl 2026 will be more exciting than ever. Guests will bid on a dazz
 ling collection of live and silent auction items as well as enjoy Calistog
 a AVA wines and desserts. Here’s a “taste” of the items up for aucti
 on: A staycation at a private residence at the Four Seasons\; a private Si
 p & Paint party at Calistoga Art Center\, curated wine collections and tas
 tings\, special dining experiences\, fine art and craft pieces in various 
 media\, and more.\n\nProceeds from the event will directly support ongoing
  art programs for the community\, including those designed for children\, 
 teens\, and seniors. Funds raised will also help cover administrative expe
 nses to operate the CAC as well as critical capital improvements to its fa
 cility. \n\nTickets are $125 each and available online at www.calistogaar
 tcenter.org/events or by calling 707-942-2278. Each event ticket includes 
 a handmade ceramic bowl to take home\, an unlimited soup tasting\, charcut
 erie\, bread\, and cookies. Wine tickets will be available for purchase. E
 ach guest will be assigned a designated table to ensure smooth and organiz
 ed seating and you can request seating with friends.  Creative center pie
 ces and table numbers will be designed by CAC students.
LOCATION:Calistoga Boys & Girls Club
URL:https://calistogaartcenter.org/souper-bowl-2026
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
