DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T180000
UID:260206AWQjbhd6WU2Feo05R0nhVA
DESCRIPTION:*Where unforgettable wines\, live music\, and good vibes come 
 together.*\n\nJoin us every Saturday from 3–6 PM at Spicy Vines for a ta
 sting room experience like no other — where top local musicians from acr
 oss the Bay Area meet our award-winning small-lot wines. From Rock & Roll 
 and Blues to Jazz\, Bluegrass\, and Americana\, each weekend brings new so
 unds and new reasons to raise a glass. \n\n**Jenerator** Jenerator is a 
 Northern California jam band duo blending rock\, funk\, blues\, and soul i
 nto powerful live performances full of heart\, rhythm\, and groove. \n\n*
 *Details**\n\nNo cover. Walk-ins are welcome\, but this event tends to fil
 l up quickly\, so we recommend making a reservation. We are dog and family
  friendly!
