UID:260327AqNR2wFQvEKjIGdzaZm8tw
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we unveil our newly remodeled Windsor store with a 
 Spring Block Party! We’ve refreshed every corner to serve you better\, a
 nd we’re celebrating with a massive community bash featuring live vendor
  demos from industry favorites like Weber\, Stihl\, Milwaukee\, and more\,
  plus food samples\, giveaways\, and prizes. To thank our community\, we a
 re picking up the tab on sales tax for the entire day. You’ll also find 
 exclusive\, event-only offers storewide\, including free BBQ supplies and 
 potting soil with qualifying purchases\, and a free engraved pet tag with 
 any $50+ pet department spend. Come explore the new space\, meet your neig
 hbors\, and join us for a day of festivities designed just for you.
