DESCRIPTION:**An intimate\, mountaintop experience designed for those who 
 love great wine\, beautiful landscapes\, and moments that feel truly speci
 al.**\n\n**Join us on *Sunday\, April 19\, 2025\,* for a day that takes 
 you high above Alexander Valley to explore Pine Mountain through the lens 
 of wine\, place\, and people. This curated experience brings together swee
 ping views\, unreleased barrel tastings\, and relaxed\, thoughtful hospita
 lity — all led by winemaker Doug Hackett himself.**\n\n**You’ll begi
 n with a welcome wine and bites as you take in the breathtaking scenery\, 
 followed by an intimate barrel tasting of unreleased wines from Spicy Vin
 es and Pine Mountain Vineyards. Afterward\, we’ll settle in for a laid-
 back BBQ lunch\, generous pours\, and easy conversation — the kind that 
 only happens when you slow down and savor where you are.**\n\n**This isn
 ’t just another tasting. It’s a rare opportunity to experience Pine Mo
 untain in a way few ever do.**
LOCATION:Spicy Vines Winery
