  sign up for both Handbuilding workshops\n\nIf you register for Dive Deepe
 r as well as Handbuilt Pots you can receive 20% off your total registratio
 n cost. Both classes are on the same day and run April 1 – May 6. There 
 will be a 30 minute break between sessions. You can call the front desk at
  \\(707\\) 938-4626 or email sean@sonomacommunitycenter.org to receive the
  discount.
