UID:2603245lrgBXDo5EGgJ4AHm1Wv0w
DESCRIPTION:Water you doing to honor Earth Day this year?\n\nJoin Daily Ac
 ts to help install over 500 low-water use\, habitat providing plants at Ci
 ty Hall's newly transformed landscape. This planting day will be one of th
 e final steps for City Hall to be a demonstration of a climate resilient g
 arden!\n\nWe'll highlight the multiple water saving features that are inst
 alled on site and will discuss how you too could implement these practices
  into your own landscape while taking advantage of local rebates and resou
 rces.\n\nLunch will be provided for all volunteers—just bring your enthu
 siasm\, and we’ll provide the rest!
