DESCRIPTION:Regenerative Ayurvedic Yoga with Tirza Dawn Come\, step onto y
 our mat with an open heart and an open mind. Invest in your self care and 
 join us for morning yoga in the OCA studio. $20 per class\, $15 for OCA me
 mbers. Each Wednesday from 9:00-10:15 AM in our Studio. Pay at the door fo
