BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Clover Sonoma Family Fun Series: Dinosaur World Live
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T183000
UID:250722OtcUZX8XEUS65t5zq6qeNw
DESCRIPTION:Back to All Shows\n\nClover Sonoma Family Fun Series\n\nDinosa
 ur World Live\n\nThursday\, April 23\, 2026\n\n6:30 pm\n\nBUY TICKETS \n\n
 Individual Tickets go on sale for Members beginning August 19\; General Pu
 blic\, August 22 \n\n \n\nDare to experience the dangers and delights of D
 inosaur World Live in this Olivier award-winning interactive show for all 
 the family. Adventurers all\, grab your compass and join our intrepid expl
 orer across uncharted territories to discover a pre-historic world of asto
 nishing \\(and remarkably life-like\\) dinosaurs. Meet a host of impressiv
 e creatures\, including every child’s favorite flesh-eating giant\, the 
 Tyrannosaurus Rex\, a Triceratops\, Giraffatitan\, Microraptor\, and Segno
 saurus! Don’t miss this entertaining and mind-expanding jurassic adventu
 re\, live on stage. \n\nRecommended for ages 5 and up\, however\, you know
  your child best. \n\nRun Time: 60 minutes\n\n \n\nLap passes available da
 y of the show\, in-person at the ticket office for ages 2 and under. \n\nL
 BC performance may not include pieces from above video. \n\n \n\nFamily Fu
 n in the Lobby\n\nStarting one hour before each performance\, please join 
 us in the lobby for fun art projects uniquely developed for each show. It
 ’s a fun\, free way for adults and children alike to get creative\, whil
 e enhancing your enjoyment of the show. We also have pizza\, beverages\, a
 nd snacks available\, all priced with a family’s budget in mind!   \n\n
 VIPs Meet the Cast\n\nSubscription holders be sure to stick around after 
 the show to meet the cast and get autographs! \\(Except The Peking Acrobat
 s®.\\) \n\n Family Fun Series – Save 20% and see all 5 shows!\n\nSee th
 e full series here: Clover Sonoma Family Fun Series \n\nTimeline\n\nNew Su
 bscriptions go on sale for Members beginning June 24\; General Public\, Ju
 ne 27.\n\nIndividual Tickets go on sale for Members beginning August 19\; 
 General Public\, August 22.\n\nTwo ways to buy! Season ticket packages are
  available online or by downloading the form \\(linked below\\) and sendin
 g the completed form to us by mail or email. If you have any questions\, c
 all the Patron & Member Services Office at 707.546.3600. \n\nPurchase New 
 Subscription ONLINE\n\nDownload New Subscription Form \n\nTHIRD PARTY RESE
 LLERS\n\nDon’t get taken by deceptive online resellers who use bots to b
 uy tickets and then mark up their prices. The only safe way to protect you
 r purchase and guarantee the best seats at the lowest cost is to work dire
 ctly with us: through our website\, by phone\, or at our box office in San
 ta Rosa. Plus\, we’re not bots. Our friendly team members are easily acc
 essible by phone or at the box office to provide customer support.
LOCATION:Luther Burbank Center for the Arts
URL:https://lutherburbankcenter.org/event/fam-dinosaur-world-live25/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Meets
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T213000
UID:260113NuC1Op5bpkqSiVSFS5aZbA
DESCRIPTION:Live models\, 5-minute to 20-minute poses. All experience & sk
 ill levels welcome. Bring your own drawing or watercolor materials. This i
 s not an instructional class.\n\nFounded more than thirty years ago by Bil
 l Wheeler\, this group continues in his honor and is coordinated by a dedi
 cated group of local artists led by John James.\n\n$20 per person for OCA 
 members\, $25 for non-members. Payment accepted at the door\, cash or chec
 k only. No minimum requirement of participation.\n\nPlease get in touch wi
 th the coordinator before attending to ensure that there is space.\n\n\\#f
 iguredrawing\n\n\\#occidentalcenterforthearts\n\n\\#sonomacounty\n\n\\#loc
 alartistsgroup
LOCATION:Occidental Center for the Arts
