DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260423T190000
UID:260111w-CDaG80RkWb-jlPhTodCQ
DESCRIPTION:Live jazz & global grooves at Golden Hour with Collaboration J
 azz Band—plus happy hour drinks & tasty food!\n\nGolden Hour with Collab
 oration Jazz Band\n\nJoin us for a perfect summer vibe as the Collaboratio
 n Jazz Band takes the stage at Barrel Proof Lounge for Golden Hour—an ea
 rly evening hang of smooth grooves\, global rhythms\, cold drinks\, and gr
 eat food.\n\n Live Music @ 5PM  Happy Hour pricing from 4–7PM  Free p
 opcorn always  Food truck on-site with delicious eats for sale\n\nThis Au
 gust only — we’re shaking things up! Instead of their usual 4th Thursd
 ay slot\, the band will perform on Thursday\, August 21st.\n\nThe Collabor
 ation Jazz Band brings together four uniquely talented Sonoma County music
 ians from diverse musical backgrounds\, blending jazz\, African\, Brazilia
 n\, pop\, and more into one vibrant sound. It’s a collaboration in every
  sense—dynamic\, fresh\, and always fun.\n\n Featuring: David Scott •
  Randy Quan • Geoff Whyte • Tim Haggerty • special guests sitting in
  each time!\n\nCome early\, grab a seat\, sip something cold\, and let the
  music carry you into the evening.\n\nCheck out **www.barrelprooflounge.c
 om** for all sorts of good times ahead!
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/live-music-happy-hour-collaboration-jazz-
 band-4th-thursdays-tickets-1514156275179?aff=oddtdtcreator
