DESCRIPTION:Friday Night Music\, Wine & Dine at Longboard Vineyards\n\nFea
 turing Highway 12 Band & Dino’s Greek Food\n\nJoin us for a lively Frida
 y night at Longboard Vineyards in our Barrel Room\, located in downtown He
 aldsburg\, featuring live music\, award-winning wine\, and fresh Mediterra
 nean flavors. Our Music\, Wine & Dine Night pairs the high-energy\, crowd-
 pleasing sounds of Highway 12 Band with classic Greek favorites from Dino
 ’s Greek Food.\n\nHighway 12 Band brings a fun mix of danceable hits and
  familiar favorites\, creating the perfect soundtrack for a relaxed and so
 cial evening surrounded by barrels and warm winery ambiance. Enjoy Longboa
 rd’s wines by the glass or bottle while Dino’s Greek Food serves tradi
 tional Greek dishes and flavorful gyros\, made fresh on site.\n\nFriday | 
 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM Free entry\n\nPlease note: This is an over-21 event in
 side the Barrel Room. Under-21 guests and leashed pets are welcome on the 
 patio only.\n\nCome grab a seat early and enjoy a classic Sonoma County ni
 ght of great music\, great wine\, and delicious food.\n\nWine available fo
 r purchase Live music by Highway 12 Band Food by Dino’s Greek Food \\(Gr
 eek cuisine and gyros\\) Location: Longboard Vineyards Barrel Room Address
 : 5 Fitch Street\, Healdsburg\, CA 95448
LOCATION:Longboard Vineyards
URL:https://www.longboardvineyards.com
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
