DESCRIPTION:Friday Night Music\, Wine & Dine at Longboard Vineyards\n\nFea
 turing Highway 12 Band & MOMO Man\n\nJoin us for a lively Friday night at 
 Longboard Vineyards in our Barrel Room\, located in downtown Healdsburg\, 
 featuring live music\, award-winning wine\, and fresh Mediterranean flavor
 s. Our Music\, Wine & Dine Night pairs the high-energy\, crowd-pleasing so
 unds of Highway 12 Band with MoMo Man Food Truck.\n\nHighway 12 Band bring
 s a fun mix of danceable hits and familiar favorites\, creating the perfec
 t soundtrack for a relaxed and social evening surrounded by barrels and wa
 rm winery ambiance. Enjoy Longboard’s wines by the glass or bottle while
  MoMo Man brings the flavors of Himalayan and Nepalese street food to Sono
 ma County\, serving up signature momos\, savory chowmein\, fried rice\, an
 d spicy\, crowd-pleasing dishes full of bold flavor.\n\nFriday | 5:00 PM 
 – 7:00 PM Free entry\n\nPlease note: This is an over-21 event inside the
  Barrel Room. Under-21 guests and leashed pets are welcome on the patio on
 ly.\n\nCome grab a seat early and enjoy a classic Sonoma County night of g
 reat music\, great wine\, and delicious food.\n\nWine available for purcha
 se Live music by Highway 12 Band Food by MoMo Man \\(Himalayan & Nepalese 
 street food\\) Location: Longboard Vineyards Barrel Room Address: 5 Fitch 
 Street\, Healdsburg\, CA 95448
LOCATION:Longboard Vineyards
URL:https://www.longboardvineyards.com
