DESCRIPTION:🍷Passport to Dry Creek Valley | Wine and Food Festival\n\nT
 ickets are officially on sale now for the 35th anniversary of this magical
  wine and food weekend event!\n\nExperience the magic of Dry Creek Valley 
 during this immersive fun-filled spring weekend\, giving you access to 50+
  wineries over three days. Meet founders & winemakers\, sip award-winning 
 wines\, enjoy thoughtfully paired local bites\, sing along to live music\,
  take advantage of insider perks\, and so much more!\n\nMORE THAN A TICKET
