 \, founder of K. LAZ WINE COLLECTION\, this exceptional event brings toget
 her wine industry leaders and enthusiasts to raise awareness\, spark chang
 e\, and secure national funding for both Alzheimer’s and dementia resear
 ch and local care initiatives.\n\nThe Main Event commences with a walk-aro
 und wine tasting at Louis Martini Winery showcasing over 35 of California
 ’s most iconic wineries\, paired with culinary stations crafted by top S
 an Francisco Bay Area culinary talent\, Componere. Iconic wineries such as
  Bryant Estate\, Dominus\, Grace Family Vineyards\, and Spottswoode Estate
  Vineyard & Winery will be joined by rising star wineries such as Aerika E
 state\, Kinsman Eades\, Morisoli Vineyard\, and MOWE Napa Valley. The even
 ing continues with a seated wine country dinner and conclude with Inspire 
 Napa Valley’s signature live auction and paddle raise.\n\nDon't miss out
